### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/healthz

### Get All Purchases (Admin required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Purchase
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Purchase
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Purchase
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "tourId": 1,
  "tourName": "Sample Tour",
  "price": 299.99,
  "purchaseDate": "2024-12-01T10:00:00Z"
}

### Get Purchase by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Purchase/{{purchaseId}}

### Get User Purchases
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Purchase/user/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Tour Purchases
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Purchase/tour/1

### Update Purchase Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/Purchase/{{purchaseId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 1
}

### Delete Purchase
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Purchase/{{purchaseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5005
@token = your_jwt_token_here
@purchaseId = purchase_id_here